  "title": "TCM Clinic Manager",
  "description": "<p>Job Description｜中医诊所店长</p><p>Location：Singapore</p><p>Position：TCM Clinic Manager</p><p></p><p>工作职责（Job Responsibilities）</p><p>1.负责中医诊所的日常运营管理，确保诊所正常、有序运作</p><p>2.管理并协调中医师、前台及诊所员工的工作安排</p><p>3.维护客户服务质量，处理预约、咨询及客户关系</p><p>4.负责诊所基本行政事务及库存管理</p><p>5.配合总部完成相关营运安排</p><p></p><p>任职要求（Job Requirements）</p><p>1.具备中医 / 医疗 / 诊所 / 健康管理相关行业经验者优先</p><p>2.有店长或诊所管理经验者优先</p><p>3.熟悉诊所日常运营流程</p><p>4.具备良好的沟通能力及团队管理能力</p><p>5.能以中文作为主要工作语言</p><p>6.工作态度稳定，责任心强</p><p></p><p>筛选问题：</p><p>1.请说明你是否具备中医 / 医疗 / 诊所相关行业经验？是否有店长或诊所管理经验？</p><p>2.你是否熟悉诊所的日常运营管理，包括人员协调、客户预约、前台流程及基本行政事务？</p><p>3.你是否可以使用中文作为主要工作语言，与客户及团队进行日常沟通？</p><p>1 Do you have prior experience in a TCM clinic, medical clinic, or healthcare-related industry? Do you have any store or clinic management experience?</p><p>2.Are you familiar with daily clinic operations, including staff coordination, appointment scheduling, front desk processes, and basic administrative duties?</p><p>3Are you able to use Mandarin Chinese as the main working language for daily communication with patients and team members?</p><p>Job Description｜TCM Clinic Manager</p><p></p><p>Location: Singapore</p><p>Position: TCM Clinic Manager</p><p>Job Responsibilities</p><p>1.Oversee the daily operations of the TCM clinic to ensure smooth and orderly operations</p><p>2.Manage and coordinate the work schedules of TCM physicians, front desk staff, and clinic personnel</p><p>3.Maintain service quality and handle appointment scheduling, enquiries, and patient relationships</p><p>4.Manage basic administrative matters and clinic inventory</p><p>5.Coordinate with head office on operational arrangements</p><p></p><p>Job Requirements</p><p>1.Prior experience in the TCM, medical, clinic, or healthcare management industry will be an advantage</p><p>2.Candidates with store or clinic management experience will be preferred</p><p>3.Familiar with daily clinic operational processes</p><p>4.Strong communication and team management skills</p><p>5.Ability to use Mandarin Chinese as the main working language</p><p>6.Stable work attitude with a strong sense of responsibility</p>",
